<p> Dear <%= @name %>;</p>
<p>We have received correspondence on a record that was directed to you as coordinator from <%=@contact.name%> at <%= @contact.email_address%>. </p>
<p>Copies went to you and all registered data managers: (<% @ccs.each do |ccs| %><%=ccs%>,<%end%>)</p>
<p>It is suggested that you take the lead in responding.</p>
<p>
<b>Content of report:</b>
<%= @contact.body %>
</p>
<% if @contact.contact_type == 'Data Problem' &&  @contact.entry_id.present?%>
<p><a href="<%=Rails.application.config.website%>/freereg1_csv_entries/<%=@contact.entry_id%>"> <%=@contact.line_id %> </a></p>
<% end%>
<p>
<b>Time:</b>
<% unless @contact.contact_time.nil? %>
<%= @contact.contact_time.strftime("%H:%M on %F") %>
<% end%>
</p>
<p>
<b>Screenshot:</b>
  <% if @contact.screenshot_url %>
    A screenshot was attached.
    <%= link_to("link",@contact.contact_screenshot_url) %><br>
  <% else %>
    No screenshot attached.
  <% end %>
</p>
<p><a href="<%=Rails.application.config.website%>/contacts/<%=@contact._id%>"> You may review the contact on line if you are logged into the system. </a></p>
<p> The <%= MyopicVicar::Application.config.freexxx_display_name %> Team</p>
